    <div class="endnote" id="ref-19"><p class="endnote-citation">19. Roberts EA, Schilsky ML. "Diagnosis and Treatment of Wilson Disease: An Update." <em>Hepatology</em> 47:2089-2111 (2008). <a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/hep.22261" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://doi.org/10.1002/hep.22261</a></p>
